Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:06.36,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Note that though we may \Nbe apart, if I am to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.84,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can I copy your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.36,Chiha-overlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No good.  What was the second verse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.80,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:13.98,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,that you pine for me as the Inaba \Nmountain pines, I shall return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:18.49,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya is a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.34,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this is your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:32.21,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:27.51,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,The first verse for this card \Nbegins with Chihaya Furu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.84,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,This is the card you pick \Nup when you hear Chihaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.88,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,so in my mind, it's the Chihaya card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:44.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:50.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:54.17,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gonna start \Nignoring you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:54.86,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.09,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ignore you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:58.05,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.33,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.65,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop talking to the outsider,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,we'll stop ignoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:17.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop ignoring \NWataya-kun instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep taking his side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:29.32,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to like about \Nthis puny and poor bumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.48,Chiha-overlap,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.36,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:29.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:39.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun can beat \Neveryone here at karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:48.62,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.56,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone take \Na single card from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you eat those words!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.97,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a showdown at the \Nupcoming karuta tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.39,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone takes a card from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.26,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're ignoring you until you graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:07.89,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a reckless bet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.31,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but it felt so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't have anything \Nwhere I could claim
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:18.31,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,that no one else could ever beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.75,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:34.92,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:34.92,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}The Red \NThat Is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:35.98,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}East Osato\N Elementary School \NKaruta Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:39.23,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:47.13,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here comes spring,\N now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.24,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why isn't anyone moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.12,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the opening poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.04,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Opening poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.60,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The contest begins with the reading
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.25,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of a poem that isn't one of the Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.65,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Then the match starts.  \NThat's what the handout said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.00,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.38,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kakinomoto no Hitomaro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:05.98,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The tail feathers of the \Ncopper pheasant are long,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.95,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.56,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.59,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.94,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.94,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.40,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.18,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:26.40,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,long as the nights I spend alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:30.31,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Next will be the first round \Nmatches for the second group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:31.31,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mashima Taichi | Tanno Shouta | Umehara Asuka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.97,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Will the contestants please \Nstep onto the tatami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.97,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were awesome, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.45,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Your next match should be just as easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.63,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:52.52,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be lame if he \Nlost in the first round?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand once \Nyou've seen him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.41,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Like a boatsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.31,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.22,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.50,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see Wataya's match?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.06,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.23,Chiha-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Does Taichi have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:45.40,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine.  \NHe can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.91,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, his mom will be \Non his case if he loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:52.39,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mashima Taichi        Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.51,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he'll have to do \Nwhatever it takes to win
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.91,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if he doesn't want to get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.76,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think he'll lose without \Ntaking a single card, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll \Nhave a perfect victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:07.32,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But you were able to \Ntake a card from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.26,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:16.35,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You have the instinct \Nof a karuta player.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The instinct of a karuta player?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.09,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.15,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.59,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?  \NIt's not poisoned or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.91,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.09,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:42.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That was his own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:54.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what's Taichi even thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't have a \Nhandkerchief on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You can wipe your face on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.73,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.59,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,It's really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.23,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Over here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.52,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get your clothes wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.17,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I run really fast, \Nthey'll dry in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.40,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:30.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.58,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:42.94,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Wataya-kun's glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.48,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.15,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:57.12,glasses,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Eyesight without glasses  0.03
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san, I'm pretty sure that Mashima
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.12,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was the one who hid my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:57.91,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi might be selfish, \Nbut he's not mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.06,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.33,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the final match!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:11.88,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.15,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have to lean \Nthat close to read them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making sure you'll \Nhave an excuse when you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.48,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just so we're clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.50,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If I take a card from you, you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:52.74,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:09:08.53,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring,\N now the flower blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.52,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain stream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.94,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.99,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.09,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.25,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he couldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.67,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.08,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.56,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He memorized the initial \Nposition of every card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.29,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My life means nothing after...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.51,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,While some dodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.91,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Wataya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:52.36,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wrong card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:58.24,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I have learned to both love and hate my fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:10:02.16,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I deflect your artful words \Nto keep my sleeves dry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.41,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.27,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:04.73,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Time to start your comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.39,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,The cards have been moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:20.09,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My fear is that you will forget \Nyour promise to never forget me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.84,Chiha-internal,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.32,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima got another card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.59,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Mashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.49,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:31.84,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When the misty bridge of magpie \Nfeathers comes into sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:29.59,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.12,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Mashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.48,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose to the outsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.87,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya's lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.85,Chiha-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for bragging \Nabout being good at karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.56,Chiha-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Take him out, Mashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.63,Chiha-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.43,Chiha-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.29,Chiha-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take Wataya-kun's place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.05,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Wataya-kun's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.10,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.58,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't interrupt \Na match, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But Sensei!  \NWataya-kun lost his glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,And um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.62,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his number one pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.38,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he doesn't \Nhave his glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya is obviously weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.76,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But Chi-chan only has a third \Nof the poems memorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.46,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:42.59,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win this \Nmatch for Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.10,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:51.84,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,the night is nearly past
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.60,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going to defeat Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.02,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,May the scarlet kadsuras \Nof Mount Afusaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.96,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I know this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.44,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.80,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to use both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What order were these in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When I was playing against Wataya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:20.76,study,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}Emperor Sutoku\NSwift waters parted by the jagged rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was focused on jumping into action
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.74,study,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(800,0)}are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as I heard the first \Nword of the first verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.96,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to keep cycling \Nthrough the first few words
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.02,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,of every first verse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.95,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what the poem means!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.35,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If she reads a card \NI don't recognize...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.43,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Since the dew atop the blades of grass
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:36.06,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I bat away the cards that are \Nin the area Taichi is looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's cheap, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I allowed to do that, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.30,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,The rules allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.00,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the correct card is \Nremoved from the area of play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.70,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This girl certainly has style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:58.86,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,For you, I head out to the \Nfields to pick spring greens
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.08,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The second verse is "while snow falls upon..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on Taichi's movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.05,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:05.44,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.97,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.14,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is she doing it for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.02,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,For that loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.05,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:19.40,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You better not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.73,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.74,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.67,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.86,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,For the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.92,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,May I find the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.25,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan got the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:47.03,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only one left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.81,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only one left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.38,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:55.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.33,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recognize any \Nof the other cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:07.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.27,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:17.10,study1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.66,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya is a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.71,Chiha-title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(700,0)}Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.18,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Impassionate gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.86,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a karuta \Nplayer sees the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.36,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.46,Chiha-main,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Our sixth grade champion is \NAyase Chihaya-san from Class 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Man!  What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.70,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if I'm not good at karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a really fun match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.03,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.03,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be a different story if
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.30,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you were playing against Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to become a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.68,Chiha-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you the Queen, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.03,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:21.56,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,It's the title given to the \Nstrongest female player.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The best player in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,is the best player in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:36.29,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you have \Nthe talent for karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:43.21,cert,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase Chihaya\NThis award certifies that you \Nperformed admirably in the\N 7th East Osato Elementary\N School Karuta Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.92,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!  Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There was a karuta tournament today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.75,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.17,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There's a scout at our house
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.71,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,right now who's interested \Nin your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:50.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:51.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.78,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He must have seen her \Nin the beauty pageant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.00,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.44,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a big dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.10,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'll throw a party for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, there was this karuta \Ntournament today and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:04.35,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...  Hurry up, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.05,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.35,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.53,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,And today, I was in \Na karuta tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.79,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.23,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.  And lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.27,Chiha-main,Chitose,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.89,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How could you lose to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.70,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was recording your matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.38,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't show this to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.84,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.51,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you \Ncan play karuta or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.01,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're going to lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.90,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're no longer allowed \Nto play in tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.62,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good student \Nand a good athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.77,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on contests that you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.41,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You beat me. \NWhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear that slam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.94,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:19.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:22.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How good is your hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.14,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was born with \Na more useful talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So I could be a good student \Nand athlete like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. \N I was born this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:36.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But I know that you made flashcards \Nfor learning the Hundred Poets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.88,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They'll think I'm lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.78,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And then I lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:45.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What's so lame about \Nlosing in a fair fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.88,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Though nobody's gonna praise \Nyou for doing well at karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.37,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need his glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Or cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:37.27,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing all alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.43,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You like playing karuta that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for your glasses again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of crows around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and one of them might have taken \Nthe glasses since they're shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the hill \Nbehind the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.36,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.67,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.03,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.51,Chiha-internal,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.13,Chiha-internal,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find Wataya-kun's glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.58,Chiha-internal,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help Wataya-kun play karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.51,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.85,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,found them in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.41,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I stole them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:00.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.87,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,her to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.69,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.94,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:20.94,cert,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A Coward
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A-A coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.51,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.12,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How many crow nests are there anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.09,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I found my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:45.03,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.03,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:50.80,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Chi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.27,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.77,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:12.08,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:18.26,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I would discover many lifelong \Ntreasures this winter.
